snippet.title: Celebrities With The Most Scientifically Beautiful Faces
snippet.description:
There’s actually a science behind why A-list celebrities are much more attractive than an average person. It may not have anything to do with makeup, facials, or hair extensions. In fact, it actually has more to do to with research and science. The more beautiful a celebrity is, the more likely they are to land large roles, and the more likely we are to enjoy seeing their faces in magazines and on screens.

Scientific research has proven that having a perfectly proportioned and balanced face can propel a celebrity’s career; people are more drawn to symmetry. Take a look at our roundup of celebrities who have the most scientifically beautiful faces in Hollywood.
